'''教宗方濟各訪美'''，是指[[天主教|天主教]][[教宗|教宗]][[方濟各_(教宗)|方濟各]]於2015年9月22日至9月27日訪問[[美國|美國]]<ref>{{Cite web|title = Viaggio Apostolico del Santo Padre a Cuba, negli Stati Uniti d'America e Visita alla Sede dell'Organizzazione delle Nazioni Unite (19–28 settembre 2015) {{!}} Francesco|url = http://w2.vatican.va/content/francesco/it/travels/2015/outside/documents/papa-francesco-cuba-usa-onu-2015.html|website = w2.vatican.va|accessdate = 2015-09-16|archive-date = 2015-09-29|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150929043743/http://w2.vatican.va/content/francesco/it/travels/2015/outside/documents/papa-francesco-cuba-usa-onu-2015.html|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="foxn_Agui">{{Cite web | title = A guide to seeing the pope in Philadelphia on the last weekend in September | author = Associated Press | work = Fox News | date = 2015-09-16 | accessdate = 2015-09-16 | url = http://www.foxnews.com/us/2015/08/16/guide-to-seeing-pope-in-philadelphia-on-last-weekend-in-september/ | quote =  | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150920231514/http://www.foxnews.com/us/2015/08/16/guide-to-seeing-pope-in-philadelphia-on-last-weekend-in-september/ | archive-date = 2015-09-20 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。該次訪問的正式名稱是「對美利堅合眾國的使徒之旅」（{{lang|en|Apostolic Journey to the United States of America}}）<ref>{{cite web|title=Schedule: 2015 Apostolic Journey Of Pope Francis To The United States Of America|date=2015-06-30|publisher=United States Conference of Catholic Bishops|accessdate=2015-09-28|url=http://www.usccb.org/about/leadership/holy-see/francis/papal-visit-2015/2015-papal-visit-schedule.cfm|archive-date=2015-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150929014020/http://www.usccb.org/about/leadership/holy-see/francis/papal-visit-2015/2015-papal-visit-schedule.cfm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，亦是方濟各就任教宗以來首次訪問美國<ref name="roll_Pope">{{Cite news | title = Pope Francis' American Crusade | last = Binelli | first = Mark | work = Rolling Stone | date = 2015-09-10 | accessdate = 2015-09-20 | url = http://www.rollingstone.com/politics/news/pope-francis-american-crusade-20150910 | language =  | quote =  | archive-date = 2015-09-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150923222909/http://www.rollingstone.com/politics/news/pope-francis-american-crusade-20150910 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，該次訪問亦成為自[[美國|美國]]與[[聖座|聖座]]兩個主權實體於1984年建立全面外交關係以來天主教教宗對美國的第七次訪問<ref name="uscc_Sche">{{cite web | title = Schedule: 2015 Apostolic Journey of Pope Francis to the United States of America | author =  | work = United States Conference of Catholic Bishops | date = 2015-06-30 | accessdate = 2015-09-09 | url = http://www.usccb.org/about/leadership/holy-see/francis/papal-visit-2015/2015-papal-visit-schedule.cfm | quote =  | archive-date = 2015-09-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150909190630/http://www.usccb.org/about/leadership/holy-see/francis/papal-visit-2015/2015-papal-visit-schedule.cfm | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title = Pope Francis Philadelphia Mass tickets go in 30 seconds - CNN.com|url = http://www.cnn.com/2015/09/09/world/pope-philadelphia-mass/index.html|website = CNN|accessdate = 2015-09-16|archive-date = 2015-09-13|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150913014152/http://www.cnn.com/2015/09/09/world/pope-philadelphia-mass/index.html|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="phil_Pope">{{Cite news|title = Pope Francis expert: Papal panic nothing new|last = Terruso|first = Julia|work = Philly.com|date = 2015-09-01|accessdate = 2015-09-20|url = http://www.philly.com/philly/blogs/real-time/Pope-Francis-expert-All-will-be-well.html|language = |quote = |archive-date = 2015-09-25|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150925144005/http://www.philly.com/philly/blogs/real-time/Pope-Francis-expert-All-will-be-well.html|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|title = Pope Francis' Visit to U.S. Is His First Ever, for Several Reasons|url = http://www.nytimes.com/2015/09/06/us/pope-francis-is-coming-to-america-after-avoiding-it-for-78-years.html|newspaper = The New York Times|date = 2015-09-05|access-date = 2015-09-06|issn = 0362-4331|first = Laurie|last = Goodstein|archive-date = 2015-09-06|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150906040027/http://www.nytimes.com/2015/09/06/us/pope-francis-is-coming-to-america-after-avoiding-it-for-78-years.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

==訪問行程==
{{UTC-4}}
方濟各完成對[[古巴|古巴]]的訪問之後，隨即開始對美國進行訪問<ref name="Catholic Herald">{{cite news|url=http://www.catholicherald.co.uk/news/2015/06/30/full-schedule-of-popes-visit-to-cuba-and-the-us-released/|title=Full schedule of Pope’s visit to Cuba and the US released|publisher=Catholic Herald|date=2015-06-30|accessdate=2015-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923135821/http://www.catholicherald.co.uk/news/2015/06/30/full-schedule-of-popes-visit-to-cuba-and-the-us-released/|archive-date=2015-09-23|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

方濟各在該次訪問中訪問[[華盛頓哥倫比亞特區|華盛頓哥倫比亞特區]]（華府）、[[紐約|紐約]]和[[費城|費城]]三個城市<ref>{{Cite web|title = Pope Francis schedule for Cuba and U.S. trips - CNN.com|url = http://www.cnn.com/2015/09/11/world/pope-francis-schedule-cuba-u-s-/index.html|website = CNN|accessdate = 2015-09-16|archive-date = 2015-09-16|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150916022026/http://www.cnn.com/2015/09/11/world/pope-francis-schedule-cuba-u-s-/index.html|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|title = Pope Francis' Schedule for His U.S. Visit|url = http://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2015/08/28/us/papal-visit-schedule.html|newspaper = The New York Times|date = 2015-09-05|access-date = 2015-09-16|issn = 0362-4331|archive-date = 2015-09-17|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150917122005/http://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2015/08/28/us/papal-visit-schedule.html|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|title = To Glimpse Pope Francis, Ticket or Patience Is Required|url = http://www.nytimes.com/2015/09/11/us/pope-francis-united-states-tickets.html|newspaper = The New York Times|date = 2015-09-10|access-date = 2015-09-16|issn = 0362-4331|first = Vivian|last = Yee|archive-date = 2015-09-15|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150915014419/http://www.nytimes.com/2015/09/11/us/pope-francis-united-states-tickets.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>。9月22日下午4時，方濟各抵達[[華府|華府]]，開始對美國的訪問，由[[美國總統|美國總統]][[巴拉克·奧巴馬|巴拉克·奧巴馬]]伉儷和[[美國副總統|副總統]][[喬·拜登|喬·拜登]]伉儷親自迎接<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.worldjournal.com/3443344/article-%E6%95%99%E5%AE%97%E6%8A%B5%E7%BE%8E%E8%A8%AA%E5%95%8F-%E6%AD%90%E5%B7%B4%E9%A6%AC%E8%A6%AA%E8%87%AA%E8%BF%8E%E6%8E%A5/|title=教宗抵美訪問 歐巴馬親自迎接|publisher=世界日報|date=2015-09-22|accessdate=2015-09-29|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150928013252/http://www.worldjournal.com/3443344/article-%E6%95%99%E5%AE%97%E6%8A%B5%E7%BE%8E%E8%A8%AA%E5%95%8F-%E6%AD%90%E5%B7%B4%E9%A6%AC%E8%A6%AA%E8%87%AA%E8%BF%8E%E6%8E%A5/|archivedate=2015-09-28}}</ref>。翌日，奧巴馬在[[白宮|白宮]]為方濟各舉行歡迎儀式，兩人其後舉行對話，談及[[貧窮|貧窮]]、[[難民|難民]]、[[暖化|暖化]]、[[墮胎|墮胎]]及[[同性婚姻|同性婚姻]]等議題，其中奧巴馬和方濟各在後兩個議題上存有分歧<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.tvb.com/world/560300546db28ce13a00000b|title=奧巴馬白宮晤教宗方濟各 舉行歡迎儀式|publisher=無綫新聞|date=2015-09-24|accessdate=2015-09-29|archive-date=2015-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151001110814/http://news.tvb.com/world/560300546db28ce13a00000b|dead-url=no}}</ref>。方濟各亦在同一天於[[聖瑪竇主教座堂_(華盛頓)|聖瑪竇主教座堂]]發表演說<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.kwongwah.com.my/?p=19579|title=方济各访美主持弥撒　不容教会发生性侵丑闻|publisher=光華日報|date=2015-09-24|accessdate=2015-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151001174907/http://www.kwongwah.com.my/?p=19579|archive-date=2015-10-01|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

9月24日，方濟各在[[美國參議院|美國參議院]]和[[美國眾議院|美國眾議院]]的聯合會議上發表講話，他亦因此成位首位在美國國會發表講話的教宗。方濟各在演說中讚揚美國前總統[[阿伯拉罕·林肯|阿伯拉罕·林肯]]和[[美國黑人民權運動|美國黑人民權運動]]領袖[[馬丁·路德·金|馬丁·路德·金]]等人，並呼籲美國對難民看成是人，而非數字<ref name=bbczh1>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world/2015/09/150924_pope_us_speech|title=教皇方济各美国国会讲话吁注意移民问题|publisher=BBC中文網|date=2015-09-24|accessdate=2015-09-29|archive-date=2015-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150927223918/http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world/2015/09/150924_pope_us_speech|dead-url=no}}</ref>。教宗在演說結束時以「天佑美國」作結，並獲得在場美國兩院議員的掌聲<ref name=bbczh1 />。演說結束之後，方濟各又使用[[西班牙語|西班牙語]]向[[國會山莊|國會山莊]]外的民眾發表講話，並聚集祈禱<ref name=bbczh1 />。其後方濟各造訪國會山莊附近一間教堂，並與遊民共晉午餐<ref name=bbczh1 />。他在聖座駐華府大使館秘密會見了因為拒絕向同性伴侶發出結婚證明而被判囚六天的[[肯塔基州|肯塔基州]]登記官[[金‧戴維斯|金‧戴維斯]]，並鼓勵她要堅強（Stay strong）。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/nation/2015/09/30/vatican-quiet-claim-pope-met-kim-davis/73078774/|title=Vatican confirms pope met with Kim Davis|publisher=今日美國報|date=2015-09-24|accessdate=2015-09-30|archive-date=2015-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151002191554/http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/nation/2015/09/30/vatican-quiet-claim-pope-met-kim-davis/73078774/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

9月25日，方濟各轉抵紐約訪問。同日上午，方濟各對[[聯合國總部|聯合國總部]]進行訪問，並在聯合國大會禮堂發表演講<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.unmultimedia.org/radio/chinese/archives/239036/#.VgtC3npViko|title=罗马天主教教皇方济各首次到访联合国—— 联大主旨演讲倡议保护环境、避免战争、弘扬博爱与人权|publisher=聯合國電台|date=2015-09-25|accessdate=2015-09-29|archive-date=2015-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151002005036/http://www.unmultimedia.org/radio/chinese/archives/239036/#.VgtC3npViko|dead-url=no}}</ref>。方濟各亦參觀[[九一一國家紀念博物館|九一一國家紀念博物館]]和[[哈林區|哈林區]]<ref name=bbczh2>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world/2015/09/150925_pope_nyc_un|title=教宗聯大發表演講呼籲尊重人類環境權利|publisher=BBC中文網|date=2015-09-25|accessdate=2015-09-29|archive-date=2015-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150929023903/http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world/2015/09/150925_pope_nyc_un|dead-url=no}}</ref>，途中經過[[中央公園_(紐約市)|中央公園]]與群眾見面<ref name=wwp>{{cite news|url=http://paper.wenweipo.com/2015/09/27/GJ1509270023.htm|title=紐約8萬人見教宗 逼爆中央公園|publisher=文匯報|date=2015-09-27|accessdate=2015-09-29|archive-date=2015-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151001050846/http://paper.wenweipo.com/2015/09/27/GJ1509270023.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。當晚，方濟各在[[麥迪遜廣場花園|麥迪遜廣場花園]]舉行彌撒，有8萬人參加該次彌撒<ref name=bbczh2 />。

9月26日，方濟各轉抵費城訪問。他首先在[[聖伯多祿聖保祿聖殿主教座堂_(費城)|聖伯多祿聖保祿聖殿主教座堂]]主持彌撒，之後又在[[美國獨立紀念館|美國獨立紀念館]]發表講話<ref name=singtaoca>{{cite news|url=http://toronto.singtao.ca/364601/2015-09-27/post-%E8%BD%89%E6%8A%B5%E8%B2%BB%E5%9F%8E%E3%80%80%E6%96%B9%E6%BF%9F%E5%90%84%E4%BF%83%E5%A5%B3%E6%95%99%E5%BE%92%E6%8D%8D%E8%A1%9B%E6%95%99%E6%9C%83/?variant=zh-hk|title=轉抵費城　方濟各促女教徒捍衞教會|publisher=多倫多星島日報|date=2015-09-27|accessdate=2015-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151001083525/http://toronto.singtao.ca/364601/2015-09-27/post-%E8%BD%89%E6%8A%B5%E8%B2%BB%E5%9F%8E%E3%80%80%E6%96%B9%E6%BF%9F%E5%90%84%E4%BF%83%E5%A5%B3%E6%95%99%E5%BE%92%E6%8D%8D%E8%A1%9B%E6%95%99%E6%9C%83/?variant=zh-hk|archive-date=2015-10-01|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。他表示，信仰自由是基本權利，並提有暴君壓制宗教自由或利用宗教宣揚仇恨和暴力。他並呼籲不同宗教信仰的人士共同發聲，追求和平，以及包容他人的尊嚴和權利，又鼓勵剛移民美國的新移民努力建立新生活<ref name=singtaoca />。之後方濟各又在[[本傑明·富蘭克林公園大道|本傑明·富蘭克林公園大道]]與參與天主教家庭節的群眾見面<ref name=wwp />。

9月27日，方濟各在[[費城藝術博物館|費城藝術博物館]]前主持露天彌撒<ref name=lhb>{{cite news|url=http://udn.com/news/story/7582/1214968-%E6%96%B9%E6%BF%9F%E5%90%84%E8%A8%AA%E7%BE%8E%E8%A1%8C-%E9%9C%B2%E5%A4%A9%E5%BD%8C%E6%92%92%E6%8E%80%E9%AB%98%E6%BD%AE|title=方濟各訪美行 露天彌撒掀高潮|publisher=聯合報|date=2015-09-28|accessdate=2015-09-29|archive-date=2015-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150930010846/http://udn.com/news/story/7582/1214968-%E6%96%B9%E6%BF%9F%E5%90%84%E8%A8%AA%E7%BE%8E%E8%A1%8C-%E9%9C%B2%E5%A4%A9%E5%BD%8C%E6%92%92%E6%8E%80%E9%AB%98%E6%BD%AE|dead-url=no}}</ref>。方濟各以西班牙語佈道，指出保護家庭是一項迫切課題，又鼓勵觀眾對「愛的奇跡」敞開心胸，他為受性侵的兒童帶來安慰，又警告美國的主教要保護信眾<ref name=lhb />。教宗在露天彌撒結束後乘專機返回[[羅馬|羅馬]]。美國副總統拜登到機場送行<ref name=lhb />。

==分析==
在方濟各訪問美國的同時，[[中華人民共和國主席|中華人民共和國主席]][[習近平|習近平]]亦[[2015年習近平訪美|訪問美國]]。台灣[[國家政策基金會|國家政策基金會]]助理研究員[[謝志傳|謝志傳]]認為，方濟各和習近平會「打個照面」，就主教任命問題和外國傳教士在中國大陸傳教的問題達成共識<ref>{{cite news|url=http://money.chinatimes.com/news/news-content.aspx?id=20150925000891&cid=1208|title=震撼 習近平與教宗傳將碰面|publisher=中國時報|date=2015-09-25|accessdate=2015-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151006065320/http://money.chinatimes.com/news/news-content.aspx?id=20150925000891&cid=1208|archive-date=2015-10-06|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。[[香港獨立媒體|香港獨立媒體]]刊登[[莫哲暐|莫哲暐]]的評論文章表示，[[中國|中國]]與[[教廷|教廷]]兩國官員可能會在9月24日在[[華府|華府]]會晤<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.inmediahk.net/node/1037587|title=教宗、習總同訪美，中梵建交可預期？|publisher=香港獨立媒體|date=2015-09-21|accessdate=2015-09-29|archive-date=2015-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151007171100/http://www.inmediahk.net/node/1037587|dead-url=no}}</ref>。但兩人最終並沒有會面<ref>{{cite news|url=http://udn.com/news/story/8299/1209810-%E4%B8%8D%E5%BC%B7%E7%A2%B0%EF%BC%81%E6%95%99%E5%AE%97%E9%9B%A2%E9%96%8B-%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E6%89%8D%E6%8A%B5%E8%8F%AF%E5%BA%9C|title=不強碰！教宗離開 習近平才抵華府|publisher=聯合報|date=2015-09-25|accessdate=2015-09-29|archive-date=2015-09-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150928030615/http://udn.com/news/story/8299/1209810-%E4%B8%8D%E5%BC%B7%E7%A2%B0%EF%BC%81%E6%95%99%E5%AE%97%E9%9B%A2%E9%96%8B-%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E6%89%8D%E6%8A%B5%E8%8F%AF%E5%BA%9C|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

教宗乘專機返回[[梵蒂岡|梵蒂岡]]時，表示期待拜訪[[中華人民共和國|中華人民共和國]]，並期待[[教廷|教廷]]與[[中國|中國]]建立良好關係的可能<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.wenweipo.com/2015/09/29/IN1509290026.htm|title=教皇再稱希望訪華:我熱愛中國人民|publisher=文匯報|date=2015-09-29|accessdate=2015-09-29|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304062711/http://news.wenweipo.com/2015/09/29/IN1509290026.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

